1
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:25,839
Dazhuang

2
00:00:26,519 --> 00:00:28,760
You went in there and got nothing on camera?

3
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:30,839
Master

4
00:00:32,399 --> 00:00:32,960
Master

5
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:34,679
You really fell asleep.

6
00:00:34,840 --> 00:00:37,280
Went in there and got nothing on camera.

7
00:00:39,479 --> 00:00:41,960
What happened after you entered the ER?

8
00:00:44,119 --> 00:00:46,119
At first, a doctor came to examine me.

9
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,439
Then they started an IV drip.

10
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:51,079
My eyelids kept getting heavier and heavier.

11
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,799
Finally, I just couldn't fight it.

12
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:54,520
And I fell asleep.

13
00:00:55,960 --> 00:00:57,079
And then?

14
00:00:58,320 --> 00:01:00,200
And then I ended up kneeling here.

15
00:01:04,359 --> 00:01:06,920
Master, what step did I get wrong?

16
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,239
Get up first.

17
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:15,560
Li Xiande's exposure put them on alert.

18
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:17,079
The experiment's been terminated.

19
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:19,239
So what do we do?

20
00:01:21,359 --> 00:01:22,400
There's another possibility.

21
00:01:23,319 --> 00:01:26,079
We got Master Zhang from Lijia Village,

22
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,359
and sent Li Qiankun in.

23
00:01:28,799 --> 00:01:30,519
The Wang Family lost their herb supplier.

24
00:01:30,599 --> 00:01:31,760
New drug production can't keep up.

25
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,560
So the experiment naturally stopped.

26
00:01:35,159 --> 00:01:36,480
But whatever the reason,

27
00:01:37,239 --> 00:01:39,599
we can't get in there to find evidence.

28
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:40,319
No.

29
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,920
We still have one option.

30
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:46,200
Lure the snake out of its hole.

31
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:50,599
Ren Feifan has been kicked out, right?

32
00:01:50,959 --> 00:01:51,239
Yes.

33
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:54,079
I had the board make it effective that day.

34
00:01:58,840 --> 00:01:59,480
Well done.

35
00:02:00,519 --> 00:02:01,519
Kill two birds with one stone.

36
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:05,079
Have you picked the new herb suppliers?

37
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,920
Most categories are already chosen.

38
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:08,800
Supplies are already coming in.

39
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,960
The rest will be secured in two weeks.

40
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,479
There shouldn't be any issue.

41
00:02:15,199 --> 00:02:16,159
What about the new drug?

42
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,560
Without the Li Family,

43
00:02:18,039 --> 00:02:20,240
secured Aconite and Pinellia Rhizome?

44
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,479
Not yet.

45
00:02:22,719 --> 00:02:25,159
I found some herb growers in remote areas.

46
00:02:25,599 --> 00:02:27,560
It's poor there, and nobody checks.

47
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,080
With enough money as bait,

48
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,120
there shouldn't be any issue.

49
00:02:32,599 --> 00:02:33,120
But...

50
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:36,560
What is it?

51
00:02:37,599 --> 00:02:39,039
Herb masters are hard to find now.

52
00:02:39,879 --> 00:02:42,360
Growing those herbs is officially banned.

53
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:46,479
So few masters can process them properly.

54
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:47,919
For the time being,

55
00:02:48,319 --> 00:02:49,639
it's hard to find one

56
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:52,520
who can process them to the old standard.

57
00:02:56,199 --> 00:02:57,479
Dad, are you all right?

58
00:02:57,759 --> 00:02:59,159
You've been coughing for a while.

59
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:00,919
I'm fine.

60
00:03:01,919 --> 00:03:03,000
What matters is the new drug.

61
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:06,520
We've bet most of our fortune on it.

62
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,599
Only if it delivers results

63
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,599
will our investment not go to waste.

64
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,280
The herb master...

65
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,240
Find one as soon as possible.

66
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:18,840
Yes.

67
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:48,479
The Princess of Xinai is in North City.

68
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,840
I hear although Xinai is a small country,

69
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,240
its royal family is super rich.

70
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,520
And this Princess of Xinai

71
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,879
is a disciple of Xinai's Medicine King.

72
00:03:57,560 --> 00:04:00,199
A princess and a disciple. Impressive.

73
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,639
Wonder what brings her to North City.

74
00:04:02,759 --> 00:04:03,680
What else could it be?

75
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:05,319
North City is the Medicine Capital.

76
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:06,400
She's here to expand her business.

77
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,680
Probably.

78
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:16,600
Dad, look at this.

79
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,720
It fell right into my lap.

80
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,959
Without any effort at all.

81
00:04:21,439 --> 00:04:23,000
The Princess of Xinai.

82
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,920
I hear this Princess of Xinai

83
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:28,000
has an incredibly powerful medical team.

84
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,519
This trip to North City

85
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,199
is for a technical exchange with us.

86
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:33,240
That's great.

87
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:35,319
I'll get some gifts and visit her.

88
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,040
Mm.

89
00:04:53,759 --> 00:04:55,720
I'm Wang Wenhao of North City Wang Group.

90
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,319
I'm here to see the Princess of Xinai.

91
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,560
We have an appointment.

92
00:04:59,199 --> 00:05:00,519
Mr. Wang, please cooperate.

93
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:02,639
Search him.

94
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,199
Please.

95
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,319
Hello, Princess.

96
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:34,360
I'm Wang Wenhao from the Wang Group.

97
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:35,720
I brought you a gift.

98
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:37,959
Pleasure to meet you, Mr. Wang.

99
00:05:38,439 --> 00:05:40,439
I've heard of Wang's medicines in Xinai.

100
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:42,639
It's a great honor.

101
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:44,600
Please, have a seat.

102
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,800
Having you visit North City

103
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,720
is truly an honor for our city.

104
00:05:59,319 --> 00:06:02,680
The Wang Group officially welcomes you.

105
00:06:08,079 --> 00:06:09,319
I hear you enjoy floral tea, Princess.

106
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:12,560
Mr. Wang.

107
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:14,759
My time is precious.

108
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,319
And I'm sure yours is too.

109
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:18,639
If you're only here to deliver a gift,

110
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:20,319
I've already received it.

111
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,319
You may take your leave now.

112
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:25,560
Here's the thing, Princess.

113
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:29,319
The Wang Group is developing a new drug.

114
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:33,000
Once launched, its potential is limitless.

115
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,160
I've heard your pharmaceutical team

116
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,240
is highly professional.

117
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:39,759
So I'm here to discuss a partnership.

118
00:06:41,639 --> 00:06:43,560
You want me to help produce your new drug?

119
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,439
It's not a one-sided request.

120
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:48,199
It's mutually beneficial, of course.

121
00:06:49,079 --> 00:06:50,160
This new drug of ours

122
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:52,480
is based on an ancient formula,

123
00:06:52,639 --> 00:06:53,839
developed into a miracle cure.

124
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:56,079
The formula is risky and unconventional.

125
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,920
But once it succeeds,

126
00:06:58,279 --> 00:06:59,439
the benefits will last for generations.

127
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,439
Oh?

128
00:07:01,279 --> 00:07:02,639
What kind of risky formula?

129
00:07:12,319 --> 00:07:14,120
Aconite and Pinellia Rhizome.

130
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,399
But as far as I know,

131
00:07:17,399 --> 00:07:18,879
these herbs are banned in your country

132
00:07:18,879 --> 00:07:20,160
from being grown or sold.

133
00:07:21,399 --> 00:07:23,160
Seems you're quite bold, Mr. Wang.

134
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:27,639
But with herbs, a miss is as good as a mile.

135
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,040
So before we partner up,

136
00:07:30,639 --> 00:07:31,759
I'd like to request, Princess,

137
00:07:32,199 --> 00:07:33,680
that we first produce some samples.

138
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:37,199
No problem.

139
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,800
But these herbs...

140
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,800
I'll deliver them as soon as possible.

141
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,600
But please understand, Princess,

142
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:47,240
these herbs are restricted in our country.

143
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,680
What I mean is,

144
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,720
I already have all these herbs.

145
00:07:52,639 --> 00:07:53,360
All of them?

146
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:54,439
Mm-hm.

147
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,759
These herbs are restricted here,

148
00:07:57,759 --> 00:08:00,199
but not in Xinai.

149
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,439
That's wonderful, Princess.

150
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:06,240
Then I'll await your good news.

151
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:07,959
I'll take my leave now.

152
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,759
The Wang Family took the bait.

153
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,199
You can start producing the new samples.

154
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,439
My dear junior brother.

155
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:40,039
This Wang Wenhao is really cunning.

156
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:43,000
Thought we'd prove he bought banned drugs.

157
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,480
But after all that runaround,

158
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,399
the Xu Family ended up signing instead.

159
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:52,679
I don't need proof of illegal drug buying.

160
00:08:54,399 --> 00:08:57,000
I need to enter his human experiment lab.

161
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,080
Try on a few more outfits.

162
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:12,720
Last time when you were hospitalized,

163
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,039
Wenhao said he didn't have time.

164
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,080
Come on.

165
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:17,840
Their family paid all your medical bills.

166
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,720
You must go thank them now.

167
00:09:19,799 --> 00:09:20,679
Hurry, pick out a few more.

168
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:21,720
Choose something nice.

169
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:23,879
Mom,

170
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,159
I don't want to try them on.

171
00:09:25,519 --> 00:09:26,360
And I'm not going.

172
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:28,960
I want to call off the engagement.

173
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,679
Did you hit your head or something?

174
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,039
He's Wang Wenhao!

175
00:09:33,399 --> 00:09:34,879
The only son of the Wang Group.

176
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:37,200
Many North City girls want to marry him.

177
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,600
And let me tell you,

178
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,960
Yesterday, I signed a contract for Wenhao.

179
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,679
With the Princess of Xinai.

180
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:46,360
Wang Wenhao and the Princess made a deal.

181
00:09:46,679 --> 00:09:49,679
The Princess is noble and vastly wealthy.

182
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,759
Both an aristocrat and a businesswoman.

183
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,159
Once he's tied to her,

184
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:55,960
Wenhao's fortune will be beyond measure.

185
00:09:56,519 --> 00:09:58,720
Listen to me, forget about Ren Feifan.

186
00:10:00,759 --> 00:10:01,360
Mom,

187
00:10:02,039 --> 00:10:04,360
Do you know why I recovered so fast?

188
00:10:05,279 --> 00:10:06,799
Feifan saved me.

189
00:10:07,399 --> 00:10:09,600
He came to give me acupuncture that night.

190
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,799
I saw him.

191
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:12,960
I've read my medical records.

192
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:14,879
My injuries were severe.

193
00:10:15,519 --> 00:10:17,759
Only his Eight Ghost Acupuncture saved me.

194
00:10:18,799 --> 00:10:21,879
But that technique shortens his lifespan.

195
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:25,519
Isn't it his duty to save you?

196
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,440
You got hurt because of him.

197
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,639
He's just expecting favors in return.

198
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,440
A rat from the gutter.

199
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,559
He just won't go away.

200
00:10:34,399 --> 00:10:34,960
Mom,

201
00:10:35,799 --> 00:10:37,559
I already owe him too much.

202
00:10:38,279 --> 00:10:40,279
Anyway, I'm not marrying Wang Wenhao.

203
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:52,240
Go tell Ren Feifan to come out here.

204
00:10:58,039 --> 00:10:58,879
Ren Feifan!

205
00:10:59,159 --> 00:11:01,639
I've never met anyone so shameless.

206
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:03,480
You just won't go away.

207
00:11:03,679 --> 00:11:04,559
I'm warning you,

208
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:06,279
Stop harassing our Ruojin.

209
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,919
A filthy stinking rat from the gutter,

210
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,440
trying to snag a rich flower.

211
00:11:12,279 --> 00:11:13,279
Our Ruojin

212
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:15,279
is going to marry Wang Wenhao.

213
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,919
She'll be the Wang Group chairman's wife.

214
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,480
You shouldn't even dream of it.

215
00:11:22,679 --> 00:11:24,159
Oh, Princess!

216
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:25,519
Princess, why are you here?

217
00:11:25,879 --> 00:11:26,759
You remember me, right?

218
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:29,000
I'm Zeng Meihua, the group rep.

219
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:29,759
You remember, don't you?

220
00:11:29,799 --> 00:11:31,120
The one who signed the contract yesterday.

221
00:11:31,399 --> 00:11:32,840
I was just curious.

222
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:35,279
Since my junior is a rat from the gutter,

223
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,320
so I came out to take a look.

224
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,840
If he's a rat from the gutter,

225
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,440
then what does that make me,

226
00:11:42,159 --> 00:11:43,399
his senior?

227
00:11:43,399 --> 00:11:43,759
This...

228
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:45,039
Feifan.

229
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,600
Princess, I didn't mean it that way.

230
00:11:46,919 --> 00:11:48,039
I didn't know you and Feifan were...

231
00:11:48,039 --> 00:11:48,879
Save your excuses.

232
00:11:49,519 --> 00:11:50,840
Take a look at the contract first.

233
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,960
It contains banned substances.

234
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:54,200
This...

235
00:11:55,519 --> 00:11:57,120
This, this, this can't be.

236
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,919
Wenhao wouldn't harm our family like this.

237
00:12:00,519 --> 00:12:02,000
You're truly blind to the truth.

238
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:04,519
It's written clearly in black and white.

239
00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:06,039
Your signature is right here.

240
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:09,559
Aconite and Pinellia Rhizome are banned.

241
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:13,399
This contract will put you behind bars.

242
00:12:14,879 --> 00:12:16,639
Feifan, please help Auntie.

243
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:18,039
You'll save me, won't you?

244
00:12:18,519 --> 00:12:19,159
Won't you?

245
00:12:19,919 --> 00:12:21,960
After all, you and Ruojin are...

246
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,320
I can withhold the evidence,

247
00:12:32,679 --> 00:12:34,879
but Auntie, you must promise me two things.
